BIB                  9         22
TITLE      Measurement and analysis of 10B+12C elastic
            scattering at energy of 41.3MeV
AUTHOR     (N.Burtebayev, M.Nassurlla, A.Sabidolda, S.B.Sakuta,
            A.A.Karakhodjaev, F.X.Ergashev, K.Rusek, E.Piasecki,
            A.Trzcinska, M.Wolinska-Cichocka, M.Kowalczyk,
            B.Mauyey, D.Janseitov, B.Zalewski, Sh.Hamada,
            K.W.Kemper, A.Ibraheem)
INSTITUTE  (4KASKAZ,4KASAFU,4RUSKUR,4UZ UZB,3POLWWA,4KASATN,
            4ZZZDUB,3EGYTNT,1USAFSU)
           (3SARSAR) King Khalid University, Abha
           (3EGYEGY) Al-Azhar University, Assiut
REFERENCE  (J,IMP/E,28,1950028,2019)
FACILITY   (CYCLO,3POLWWA) U-200P
SAMPLE     0.14 mg/cm2 thick
METHOD     (EDE)
DETECTOR   (TELES,IOCH,SI)
           Four dE-E telescopes consisting of Si detectors (E)
            about 300 um in thickness and ionization chambers
            (dE) filled with isobutene (C4H10) to a pressure of
             55.5 Torr
HISTORY    (20260316C) Sanira Turganova
           (20260316R) Received by e-mail from Maulen Nassurlla
